ISLAMABAD, Jul 15 (APP):The Federal Government has been pleased to appoint Shazia Marri, Minister for Poverty Alleviation and Social Safety as Chairperson, Benazir Income Support Programme (BISP) Board with immediate effect.
According to a notification issued on Friday, Shazia Marri will head the BISP Board untill the appointment of its regular Chairperson.
